Class FeatureEvidenceEnricherStatisticsWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.EnricherStatisticsWriter<T>
      • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.FeatureEnricherStatisticsWriter<FeatureEvidence>
        • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.FeatureEvidenceEnricherStatisticsWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, EnricherListener<FeatureEvidence>, FeatureEnricherListener<FeatureEvidence>, AliasesChangeListener<FeatureEvidence>, AnnotationsChangeListener<FeatureEvidence>, FeatureChangeListener<FeatureEvidence>, FeatureEvidenceChangeListener, IdentifiersChangeListener<FeatureEvidence>, ParametersChangeListener<FeatureEvidence>, XrefsChangeListener<FeatureEvidence>
    public class FeatureEvidenceEnricherStatisticsWriter
extends FeatureEnricherStatisticsWriter<FeatureEvidence>
implements FeatureEvidenceChangeListener
    A statistics logger which records changes made by the enricher. Each addition, removal or update is counted and, upon the completion of the enrichment of the object, is logged in either a file of successes or failures depending on the enrichmentStatus.
    Since:
    18/07/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
